headline.main: Australia Content Having Batted Entire Day, Says Renshaw
headline.print_headline: Australia Content Having Batted Entire Day, Says Renshaw

lead_paragraph: Australia are hoping to chase as little as they can in their fourth innings against India on a difficult pitch, opener Matt Renshaw said on Sunday, adding that the touring side were content with having batted for the entire second day.
